5. Registration procedure
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
   You can find registration form in following files: reg_form.txt,
reg_form.odt and reg_form.pdf.

   a. On-line registration:
      You can start the registration  procedure  with 'Configuration/On-line
      registration menu of the application.

   b. Registration in e-mail:
      Fill the registration form and send it in e-mail to the address below.

   c. Registration with telefax:
      Fill the registration form and send it on telefax to the fax number below.

   d. Registration in postal letter:
      Fill the registration form and send it in letter to the address below.

   After  you  sent the  registration form, you will receive a  confirmation e-
mail with the  amount to  be  paid and your serial number. The registration
price  depends on type of licence, you can  find  it on  registration forms.
After paying you will receive registration key and the invoice in PDF format
via e-mail.

   WARNING! If you pay via Paypal, we add its handling fee to total amount (2.9%
+ 0.25 USD).

6. Free registration
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
   If you translate the 'translate package' to any language you can get 2 pieces
personal (home use only - 1 computer) licences or 1 pc. education/non-profit
organisation (2-5 computers) licence or 1 pc. commercial licence (1 computer)
for free.

   Conditions:
   - Fill registration form and send me via e-mail for request free licenc. You
     can find it in following files: free_reg_form.txt, free_reg_form.odt or
     free_reg_form.pdf;
   - If the language, what you have specified is busy, your request will be
     rejected. I will send e-mail about it;
   - Just give free licence to the completely translated package. You will get
     serial number and keyfile after I checked the package.
   - Character set must be UTF-8.

   Content of translate package:

     README                       only 5 line
     tubes2trial.desktop          only 2 line
     documents/INSTALL            only titles
     documents/reg_form.txt
     documents/free_reg_form.txt
     documents/support_form.txt
     languages/tubes2trial.pot
     database_keywords.txt        only keywords (anode, cathode, diode etc.)

   Download: <http://www.pozsarzs.hu/tubes/tubes2_translate.zip>

   Released language packages are downloadable from homepage of project for
both (trial/pro) versions.
     
7. Project support
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
   If you are electrontube manufacturer or distributor and you want a cheap
advertisement then support Tubes2 projekt. I show your web address in menu
of Tubes2 applications and on homepage of the project
<http://www.pozsarzs.hu/tubes.html> in exchange of price of personal, home
licence.

   Conditions:
   - Fill registration form and send me via e-mail for support project. You can
     find it in following files: support_reg_form.txt, support_reg_form.odt or
     support_reg_form.pdf.
   - After  you  sent the  registration form, you will receive a  confirmation
     e-mail with the  amount to  be  paid. After paying you will receive invoice
     in PDF format.

